@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_czeces(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.30 + tmp + 0.51)) - ((v0 + 0.60 - v1 + 0.96) - (v2 + 0.45 * tmp + 0.70)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = v1
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.20 / v2 + 0.22)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(v0) + wp.abs((v1 + 0.46 - tmp + 0.43)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (v1 / wp.sin((v1 + 0.17 * v2 + 0.91)))
    v2 = (0.26 * 0.05)
    data[tid] = v0
